1) Both NATS and STAN(Nats Streaming) run the monitoring and metric containers... (Bortkommenterade nu...)
    Alt 1: Disabling monitoring and metric for Core NATS and only run them in Streaming



The working one is stan directory:
    1) Install storage class (gce_standard.storageclass.yaml)
    2) Install nats-instance (core server) (nats-instance.yaml) and wait until all are done..
    3) Install stan-instance (streaming) (stan-instance.yaml) and wait until all are done..
    4) Install NATS-Operator:
        4.1) kubectl apply -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nats-io/nats-operator/master/deploy/00-prereqs.yaml
            Alt: kubectl apply -f nats-operator1.yaml
        
        4.2) kubectl apply -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nats-io/nats-operator/master/deploy/10-deployment.yaml
            Alt: kubectl apply -f nats-operator2.yaml
    
    5) Install Prometheus-Operator:
        kubectl apply -f prometheus-operator.yaml
    6) Install NATS-cluster:
        kubectl apply -f nats-cluster.yaml
    
    7) Install Prometheus role RBAC:
        kubectl apply -f prometheus-rbac.yaml
    8) Install Prometheus instance:
        kubectl apply -f prometheus-instance.yaml

    9) Install Service Monitor:
        kubectl apply -f service-monitor.yaml
    
    10) The Prometheus Web Monitoring program runs on port 9090:
        Uses nginx for exposing the service to one of the nodes (NodePort) right now, later use LoadBalancer



http://prometheus-operated:9090/

Setup Order:
1) kubectl apply -f stan_helm/prometheus-operator-deployment.yaml -n nats
2) kubectl apply -f stan_helm/nats-operator1.yaml -n nats
3) kubectl apply -f stan_helm/nats-operator2.yaml -n nats
4) kubectl apply -f stan_helm/prometheus-rbac.yaml -n nats
5) kubectl apply -f stan_helm/nats-cluster.yaml -n nats
6) kubectl apply -f stan_helm/prometheus-operator.yaml -n nats
7) kubectl apply -f stan_helm/prometheus-instance.yaml -n nats
8) helm install -f stan_helm/nats/values.yaml -n nats my-nats ./stan_helm/nats/
9) helm install -f stan_helm/stan/values.yaml -n nats my-stan ./stan_helm/stan/
10) kubectl apply -f stan/grafana.yaml -n nats
11) kubectl apply -f stan_helm/nginx.yaml